#: paragraph:6,sentence:31
msgid "And as each one elects to join with me, the song of thanks from earth to Heaven grows from tiny scattered threads of melody to one inclusive chorus from a world redeemed from hell, and giving thanks to You.[3]"
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 7: And now, I invite you to take a brother’s or sister’s hand, find the song in your heart, and step forward to join “Bill’s chorus.” The best of this musical comedy of life is yet to come, and never aga...
#: paragraph:7,sentence:32
msgid "And now, I invite you to take a brother’s or sister’s hand, find the song in your heart, and step forward to join “Bill’s chorus.” The best of this musical comedy of life is yet to come, and never again will we forget to laugh."
msgstr ""

